* 2022.02.04    v1.0.5  Added `quote_keep` option to preserve quote marks in the output or not
* 2023.01.12    v1.0.6  Remark characters interrupt string parsing
* 2024.04.03    v1.0.7  Cosmetics to make pylint happy
